Class LiteralIndex

  • java.lang.Object
    • Datastructures.Literals.LiteralIndex

  • public class LiteralIndex
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Ohlbach on 25.08.2018. This index maps literals (integers) to their CLiterals (clause occurrences)
